(123, 'Laminate cleaner-750 ml', '', '<p><strong>1. Product Description</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mild neutral cleaning agent for the initial and regular cleaning of laminate floors. Removes dirt, fat,</p>\r\n<p>grease and shoe marks. Does not leave a residue. For EN 13329-defined laminate floor coverings and</p>\r\n<p>laminate surfaces (including kitchen and bathroom furniture). Specifically developed for all click</p>\r\n<p>laminate floors.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. Areas of Application</strong></p>\r\n<p>All kinds of laminated floors and surfaces (e.g. furniture in kitchen and bathroom).</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. Method of Application</strong></p>\r\n<p>Dilute Laminate Cleaner in a ratio of 1:200 (50 ml to 10 l of water) and lightly damp wipe over the</p>\r\n<p>floor with this solution. For larger surface areas use a dilution up 1:200 to 1:400 using the spraycleaning</p>\r\n<p>method in combination with a monodisc machine such as the SRP 1 plus a white or red</p>\r\n<p>pad. Glue residues and stubborn stains can be removed with Elatex Universal Stain Remover.</p>\r\n<p>Consumption: 1 l = 1000 m&sup2;</p>\r\n<p>Note: Laminated floors or surfaces should never be damp or wet for a longer period of</p>\r\n<p>time. Especially the edges could swell up and change shape. Therefore always wipe</p>\r\n<p>with thoroughly wrung-out cloths and ensure that no &ldquo;pools&rdquo; are created on the</p>\r\n<p>floor.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. Technical Data</strong></p>\r\n<p>pH level: approx. 7.5</p>\r\n<p>Product code for cleaning and care products (Giscode): GU 50</p>\r\n<p>Data on ingredients (EC recommendation): less than 5% anionic surfactants, non-ionic surfactants.</p>\r\n<p>Contains BENZISTHIAZOLINONE, METHYLISOTHIALZOLINONE, perfume, CITRAL, LIMONENE,</p>\r\n<p>LINALOOL, solvents.</p>\r\n<p>Laminate Cleaner should be stored in a cool, dry place in its closed original container. Protect from</p>\r\n<p>frost. Keep locked up and out of the reach of children.</p>\r\n<p><strong>www.dr-schutz.com</strong></p>', '', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="../uploads/top_logo.gif" alt="" width="344" height="76" /></p>', '', 3, 0, 0, 27, '2014-12-29', 27, 20, 9, 20, '', 0, 0, 0, 'Laminate cleaner', '', ''),
